fields.description: Buying handmade also means buying products which are  unique!
We shape clay into a pot, but it is the emptiness inside that holds whatever we want.
Life is too short to wear mass market clothes, choose Hand Made.
You can't buy LOVE, but you can buy Handmade and that's kind of the same thing.
